member.summary:
Fluent builder for generating .htaccess files that control directory
security and access when used with  or
.


Example usage:

server.Http.MapDirectory("/Update", updateDir, htaccess => {
    htaccess
        .DenyDirectoryListing()
        .AllowFrom("192.168.1.0/24")
        .DenyFiles("*.log", "*.bak")
        .RequireBasicAuth("Admin Area", "admin", "secret");
});

Dispatches  on the UI / main thread.
On WPF, verifies  is still alive;
if the application has already shut down, calls  instead.
